reviewText:
I enjoyed this film -it is a fun watch, even though the story is cliched -father of girl does not like boy his daughter
likes.  BUT buyer beware -THIS IS ONLY FIRST HALF OF FILM- the second half is TIMEPASS 2 which doesn't
seem to be available in USA.  A very well made film - hope I can get a copy of TIMEPASS 2 some day?
